---
description: Shared project rules for the portfolio repository
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` before making changes.

This is a public portfolio repository. Do not commit private notes, research, inspiration, raw prompts, secrets, local screenshots, personal documents, proprietary fonts, or environment files.

Preserve app behavior unless the task requires a change. Keep changes small, accessible, responsive, and consistent with the existing design system.

Do not add AI or agent co-authorship to commits. No `Co-authored-by:` trailers and no "Generated with" agent attribution. See AGENTS.md, "Commit conventions".

Use `docs/agent-handoff.md` for sanitized handoff notes.
